WEBVTT

01:48.600 --> 01:50.200
Freeze! Stop right there!

01:50.760 --> 01:52.800
Stay where you are!
Move again, and I'll shoot!

01:52.880 --> 01:54.280
Don't shoot! Please!

01:54.360 --> 01:55.920
We surrender!

01:56.000 --> 01:57.360
‎My goodness.

02:00.400 --> 02:04.840
DIE

02:23.840 --> 02:24.960
What are you laughing at?

02:25.720 --> 02:26.560
Enjoy the foot-soaking water?

02:42.920 --> 02:43.640
Officer He. We…

02:43.720 --> 02:45.720
-We met before.
-We met before.

02:45.800 --> 02:48.160
Do I know you? Did I arrest you before?

02:48.240 --> 02:50.080
-Yesterday afternoon. Yesterday afternoon.
-Afternoon.

02:50.160 --> 02:52.040
-I just saw you.
-We met.

02:53.280 --> 02:54.640
TRANSFORM BUSINESS FOR GROWTH

02:58.720 --> 02:59.920
You work for Jin Manshan?

03:00.840 --> 03:02.240
Then why didn't you
tell the truth yesterday?

03:02.320 --> 03:04.320
Are you involved
with the missing father and daughter?

03:04.920 --> 03:06.040
Nothing to do with us!

03:06.120 --> 03:08.120
-We just came here to take a look.
-We are just…

03:08.200 --> 03:08.880
What does that have to do with anything?

03:08.960 --> 03:09.880
-Nothing.
-Nothing.

03:09.960 --> 03:11.040
Shut up!

03:11.120 --> 03:12.160
One at a time.

03:12.800 --> 03:13.880
You go first.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.320
We… We're just…

03:16.000 --> 03:17.960
-We're just part-timers.
-Part-timers.

03:18.040 --> 03:19.480
Part-timers?

03:19.560 --> 03:20.560
What kind of "part-timers"
walk around with tattoos

03:20.640 --> 03:21.880
and carry stuff like that?

03:21.960 --> 03:23.520
We don't know anything.

03:23.600 --> 03:26.040
We just spent 200 yuan to get the tattoos,

03:26.120 --> 03:27.960
so we could go collect debts.

03:28.040 --> 03:29.400
You came here to collect money?

03:30.440 --> 03:32.320
How much does the Xu family
owe Jin Manshan?

03:32.400 --> 03:34.040
Two hundred and fifty thousand.

03:34.560 --> 03:35.440
How much did they actually borrow?

03:37.280 --> 03:38.320
Eight thousand.

03:40.760 --> 03:44.240
You loan sharks are real math geniuses.

03:46.640 --> 03:48.320
This isn't your first time here, is it?

03:48.400 --> 03:49.440
Yesterday afternoon.

03:49.520 --> 03:51.280
-Afternoon.
-We came yesterday afternoon.

03:51.360 --> 03:56.280
DIE

03:56.360 --> 03:57.200
Are you sure?

03:57.800 --> 03:58.680
No one is home.

03:58.760 --> 04:00.360
What's the point of writing that?

04:00.440 --> 04:01.960
You're so clueless.

04:02.040 --> 04:04.040
I wrote this to show Mr. Jin.

04:05.000 --> 04:06.320
Sling it over your shoulder. Quick.

04:22.160 --> 04:25.120
DAJIANCHANG NEIGHBORHOOD

04:25.800 --> 04:27.280
-I'm hungry.
-How about

04:27.360 --> 04:29.960
we go grab something to eat?

04:40.240 --> 04:41.480
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

04:42.360 --> 04:45.920
-We went out to get some tofu pudding.
-We ate tofu pudding.

04:46.000 --> 04:48.680
-Then we came back.
-We saw the tape had been removed.

04:48.760 --> 04:49.960
-We thought the family had returned.
-We thought…

04:50.040 --> 04:51.280
Enough.

04:51.360 --> 04:52.600
Are you two performing crosstalk?

04:53.200 --> 04:54.040
When was the last time

04:54.120 --> 04:55.440
the father and daughter
were seen leaving home?

04:55.520 --> 04:58.640
People said it was the day
before Hong Kong, China's handover.

04:58.720 --> 05:00.080
Someone saw them leave,

05:00.160 --> 05:02.160
-and they never came back.
-Never came back.

05:03.520 --> 05:05.120
30TH, MONDAY

05:11.000 --> 05:12.520
Why did the Xu family borrow money?

05:13.440 --> 05:15.040
-Because…
-You answer.

05:15.120 --> 05:16.800
The daughter was devoted.

05:16.880 --> 05:18.360
She borrowed money to treat her father.

05:18.440 --> 05:20.080
Her father was in poor health.

05:20.160 --> 05:23.000
The medical bills
drained everything they had.

05:23.080 --> 05:23.960
What illness?

05:24.760 --> 05:25.600
No idea.

05:30.800 --> 05:32.520
-We don't know.
-We really don't know.

05:32.600 --> 05:33.520
We honestly don't know.

05:44.560 --> 05:45.720
You were carrying a gun just now.

05:45.800 --> 05:47.480
Did you file the paperwork to borrow it?

05:50.200 --> 05:53.240
FOR DRAMATIC EFFECT. DO NOT IMITATE

05:53.320 --> 05:54.360
What are you doing?

05:56.240 --> 05:57.440
What are you doing exactly?

05:58.400 --> 06:00.080
That's pure reflex.

06:00.160 --> 06:02.960
When criminals hear a gunshot,
they assume it's real.

06:03.600 --> 06:04.800
What?

06:05.760 --> 06:07.400
Reflex.

06:08.040 --> 06:10.160
A real cop using a fake fun?
And you're proud of it.

06:10.240 --> 06:11.800
As long as it works.

06:11.880 --> 06:13.480
You nearly scared me to death.

06:14.080 --> 06:16.360
The Xu father and daughter
might've gone to relatives to dodge debt.

06:16.440 --> 06:17.920
I want to check their household records.

06:18.000 --> 06:20.040
Do you know what time it is?
The registry office isn't open yet.

06:21.200 --> 06:23.280
Two more hours. I'll wait.

06:25.400 --> 06:28.000
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY

06:40.760 --> 06:43.280
You dressed like
some imperial envoy on tour.

06:43.360 --> 06:45.560
Chasing suspects
in leather shoes and slacks?

06:45.640 --> 06:47.200
That's not practical.

07:25.760 --> 07:28.280
Timing matters more than being early.

07:29.000 --> 07:30.040
Oh my!

07:35.520 --> 07:38.240
He Yuanhang, what happened to you?

07:38.840 --> 07:41.560
Paint. I brushed against it.

07:42.200 --> 07:43.400
Brushed against it?

07:43.960 --> 07:46.600
Looks like you fell into a paint vat.

07:46.680 --> 07:48.360
That's what being a detective is like.

07:48.440 --> 07:50.240
Dirty, exhausting, and rough.

07:50.320 --> 07:52.800
-You never know what tomorrow will bring.
-Go wash up.

07:53.400 --> 07:55.840
Dad, you've changed.

07:56.600 --> 07:59.000
Ever since you joined
the criminal department,

07:59.080 --> 08:01.240
you've been talking big.

08:02.320 --> 08:04.880
Kiddo, I promise you.

08:04.960 --> 08:06.880
I'll prove it soon enough.

08:11.640 --> 08:12.680
That hairstyle is cool.

08:12.760 --> 08:15.320
When I grow up, I want one like that too.

08:23.280 --> 08:28.440
MODERN LAW ENFORCEMENT
UNWAVERING POLICE EXCELLENCE

08:31.560 --> 08:33.159
-Morning, Captain Zhao, Captain Qu.
-Morning.

08:34.000 --> 08:35.039
Captain Zhao.

08:41.440 --> 08:44.000
The case in Binchuan District,
where four teenagers had gone missing,

08:44.080 --> 08:45.400
has been going on for almost two weeks.

08:45.480 --> 08:47.000
We still haven't found them.

08:47.080 --> 08:49.400
All kinds of rumors are spreading online,

08:49.480 --> 08:51.360
and it's causing quite a stir.

08:51.440 --> 08:52.800
-Director Zou mentioned…
-I know.

08:52.880 --> 08:54.280
He already called me.

08:54.360 --> 08:56.360
We'll be assisting the municipal bureau
on this joint case.

08:56.440 --> 08:59.520
-Qu. You take this case.
-Alright.

08:59.600 --> 09:00.440
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

09:00.520 --> 09:03.160
Contact all stations in our jurisdiction.
Get them involved too.

09:03.240 --> 09:04.600
No problem.

09:04.680 --> 09:05.880
We all know each other. They'll cooperate.

09:05.960 --> 09:07.520
Report to me immediately
when there are any solid leads.

09:07.600 --> 09:08.520
Understood, Captain Zhao.

09:09.640 --> 09:10.720
Captain Zhao.

09:11.840 --> 09:13.840
-Good morning.
-Morning.

09:15.400 --> 09:18.000
Captain Zhao, about the report
I submitted earlier,

09:18.080 --> 09:20.160
when would you have time to approve it?

09:22.000 --> 09:23.000
What report?

09:23.080 --> 09:25.400
The application for field duty.

09:29.640 --> 09:30.480
Xiaohe,

09:31.200 --> 09:33.320
field work is tough,

09:33.400 --> 09:34.920
exhausting, and dangerous.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.560
Captain Zhao, I'm not afraid.

09:36.640 --> 09:38.120
I studied criminal investigation
for six years.

09:38.200 --> 09:39.560
Fieldwork is exactly what I'm trained for.

09:44.320 --> 09:45.160
Oh, well.

09:46.160 --> 09:48.080
If only you showed that same dedication

09:48.160 --> 09:50.600
to taking care of your dad.

09:51.120 --> 09:52.200
-Captain Zhao.
-But…

09:52.280 --> 09:53.960
The report you requested is ready.

09:56.240 --> 09:57.480
Come with me.

09:57.560 --> 09:59.680
Does Han Zi'ang have a phone or a camera?

09:59.760 --> 10:01.000
No.

10:01.960 --> 10:04.040
There's not much to do at Yuanlongli.

10:04.120 --> 10:06.440
People mostly go there
to take photos and videos.

10:06.520 --> 10:08.480
If your child doesn't have
a phone or a camera,

10:08.560 --> 10:09.480
it's unlikely he went there.

10:10.080 --> 10:11.840
Here's what you do.
Go home and wait for now.

10:11.920 --> 10:13.440
Maybe he skipped class
and went out to play.

10:13.520 --> 10:15.200
That's impossible.

10:15.280 --> 10:16.960
I met a psychic this morning.

10:17.040 --> 10:20.080
He said Ang must be in Yuanlongli.

10:20.160 --> 10:22.480
A psychic? That's all nonsense.

10:22.560 --> 10:24.240
Why would a psychic lie?

10:24.320 --> 10:26.160
He promised to help me find my child.

10:26.240 --> 10:29.520
Ma'am, what did this psychic look like?

10:29.600 --> 10:30.800
He…

10:30.880 --> 10:32.240
He is about this tall,

10:32.320 --> 10:34.840
wearing a colored shirt,
and carrying a bag.

10:34.920 --> 10:36.920
He said all the missing kids in Yuanlongli

10:37.000 --> 10:38.240
were found by him.

10:43.320 --> 10:44.400
Han Zi'ang.

10:45.560 --> 10:46.960
Come out.

10:47.040 --> 10:49.000
Your mom's looking for you.

10:51.560 --> 10:53.560
Now that Yuanlongli
is about to be demolished,

10:54.440 --> 10:57.320
everything hidden inside
will come out into the open.

11:01.000 --> 11:04.360
DEMOLITION

11:16.680 --> 11:20.280
You see,
if you hadn't gone to Beijing back then,

11:20.920 --> 11:22.440
would things between you two…

11:22.520 --> 11:23.720
No.

11:26.920 --> 11:28.240
And there's no "if".

11:30.960 --> 11:32.800
I've always wondered.

11:33.400 --> 11:35.080
You two were such a good match.

11:35.680 --> 11:37.560
What happened in the end?

12:14.720 --> 12:16.320
Where did the trike go?

12:18.920 --> 12:20.000
What trike?

12:20.520 --> 12:21.920
Are you remembering it wrong?

12:23.120 --> 12:24.400
No way.

12:24.480 --> 12:27.000
It was blocking the door.
I moved it myself.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.720
Someone must've been here.

12:36.800 --> 12:38.960
-Let's go back and check.
-Sir.

13:25.280 --> 13:27.360
MISSING PERSON

13:35.120 --> 13:36.000
You're here.

13:39.240 --> 13:40.400
What are you doing here?

13:42.480 --> 13:44.800
What kind of question is that?
I'm here to work.

13:45.920 --> 13:47.200
Did you track down
their household registration?

13:49.840 --> 13:51.680
The Xu's have two relatives in Weiyang.

13:51.760 --> 13:54.040
Xu Zhihong has a sister. Xu Meng
has an uncle on her mother's side.

13:54.120 --> 13:55.800
XU MEIQIN'S AND QIAO GUOQIANG'S ADDRESSES

13:58.720 --> 14:00.640
Let's split up. Make it quick.

14:05.920 --> 14:08.800
I don't have a brother like that.
And no niece either.

14:11.720 --> 14:15.080
Xu Meng borrowed money from you
to treat her father, right?

14:15.160 --> 14:18.080
To be honest, in my brother's condition,

14:18.160 --> 14:19.680
he'd be better off dead.

14:19.760 --> 14:20.800
It's done.

14:23.240 --> 14:25.120
-Alright. Have a nice day.
-Thank you.

14:26.840 --> 14:29.600
He couldn't pay the debt,
so he kept pestering me.

14:29.680 --> 14:32.960
Look around. This place is a mess.

14:33.040 --> 14:35.400
When was the last time you saw them?

14:35.480 --> 14:37.880
Last year, one night.
He suddenly had an attack.

14:37.960 --> 14:40.080
Meng brought him over to borrow money.

14:41.760 --> 14:43.040
Aunt.

14:44.200 --> 14:46.160
Open the door, Aunt.

14:46.680 --> 14:47.680
Aunt.

14:47.760 --> 14:48.800
Aunt.

14:49.640 --> 14:52.520
-Meng.
-Aunt, my dad's sick again.

14:56.040 --> 14:57.160
Slow down.

15:05.400 --> 15:07.640
Aunt, could you…

15:18.040 --> 15:19.280
Thank you, Aunt.

15:21.040 --> 15:21.880
Meng.

15:23.920 --> 15:26.520
I'm planning to move away soon.

15:27.520 --> 15:28.720
Where are you moving to?

15:41.320 --> 15:42.600
I understand.

15:42.680 --> 15:44.560
I won't come again.

15:44.640 --> 15:48.280
I'll find a way to pay you back.

15:56.560 --> 15:58.600
Take this. Go to the hospital now.

15:59.120 --> 16:00.280
Thank you, Aunt.

16:12.240 --> 16:13.920
She's a good kid.

16:14.920 --> 16:16.880
Definitely.

16:18.320 --> 16:19.240
What a shame.

16:19.320 --> 16:21.680
She got dragged down by her father.

16:24.680 --> 16:25.960
To be frank,

16:26.040 --> 16:27.920
when I heard my brother had gone missing,

16:28.000 --> 16:32.480
I actually felt relieved.

16:33.240 --> 16:36.040
I shouldn't have felt that way.

16:38.960 --> 16:40.960
Life and death aren't up to us.

16:41.040 --> 16:43.080
Not up to us?

16:43.160 --> 16:45.840
He brought this on himself.

16:45.920 --> 16:47.960
He was perfectly fine before.

16:48.040 --> 16:48.880
But two summers ago,

16:48.960 --> 16:51.160
he and his daughter
went to Mount Wu for a trip,

16:51.240 --> 16:53.360
like they were possessed.

16:53.960 --> 16:55.480
They ran into an accident
in the mountains.

16:55.560 --> 17:00.480
He fell off a cliff
and ended up like this.

17:00.560 --> 17:02.960
Half dead.

17:03.040 --> 17:05.880
A mountain accident?
The Mount Wu incident?

17:05.960 --> 17:08.119
MAJOR MOUNTAIN ACCIDENT HIT MOUNT WU
KUNHAI CITY, YESTERDAY

17:08.200 --> 17:10.319
It started with heavy rain,
then thick fog.

17:10.400 --> 17:13.520
That tour group got lost
the moment they entered the mountains.

17:13.599 --> 17:15.079
You can imagine. In the mountains,

17:15.160 --> 17:17.040
there was no food, no water,

17:17.560 --> 17:18.839
and no one coming to help.

17:19.839 --> 17:21.599
Many people froze to death.

17:22.119 --> 17:23.760
My uncle was one of the lucky ones.

17:23.839 --> 17:25.280
He made it out alive.

17:25.359 --> 17:26.599
He might as well be dead!

17:31.280 --> 17:33.960
That's how Xu Zhihong
ended up with his condition.

17:37.520 --> 17:40.240
-Can I borrow this newspaper?
-Take that.

17:40.760 --> 17:42.240
Why are you keeping
that frigging paper anyway?

17:44.760 --> 17:47.600
When was the last time you saw Xu Meng?

17:48.200 --> 17:49.320
When?

17:49.840 --> 17:51.240
Heaven knows how long ago!

17:53.960 --> 17:56.520
Officer, want me to pour you some tea?

18:19.960 --> 18:21.720
Does anyone in your family do this too?

18:23.160 --> 18:24.120
No, I just like it.

18:31.000 --> 18:31.960
Young man,

18:32.680 --> 18:35.360
do you think people are afraid
of dying at the end?

18:38.680 --> 18:40.040
I don't really know.

18:40.800 --> 18:42.080
Look at my brother-in-law.

18:42.160 --> 18:43.560
He can barely breathe.

18:43.640 --> 18:45.200
Living like that is worse than dying.

18:45.280 --> 18:47.920
So why keep him alive?

18:48.000 --> 18:49.760
Last winter, I cut ties with them.

18:50.360 --> 18:51.840
Just to keep him alive,

18:51.920 --> 18:53.320
the father and daughter scammed people.

18:53.400 --> 18:55.480
She even turned to prostitution
and worked as a hostess.

18:55.560 --> 18:58.480
Anyone tied to relatives like that
is doomed.

18:58.560 --> 18:59.840
Don't talk about Meng like that.

18:59.920 --> 19:01.040
Why not?

19:01.120 --> 19:02.720
Didn't Xu Meng take advantage of you?

19:03.240 --> 19:05.360
You lent her your wedding money.

19:05.440 --> 19:07.400
She said she'd pay it back
right away. Did she?

19:08.000 --> 19:09.880
And your engagement fell apart.

19:09.960 --> 19:11.320
You really don't know why?

19:25.440 --> 19:28.560
Do you know if they crossed
the wrong people?

19:30.000 --> 19:30.840
Probably loan sharks.

19:33.160 --> 19:34.360
My uncle is actually a good man.

19:34.440 --> 19:36.560
He raised Meng all by himself.

19:36.640 --> 19:38.080
It wasn't easy.

19:39.320 --> 19:41.720
So Xu Zhihong was a loving father?

19:41.800 --> 19:43.720
Loving, you say? More like a "treasure".

19:43.800 --> 19:45.800
He's in that state and still not dead.

19:45.880 --> 19:47.200
I'd say he's some treasure indeed.

19:47.280 --> 19:48.680
Dad!

19:52.320 --> 19:54.520
MAJOR MOUNTAIN ACCIDENT HIT MOUNT WU
KUNHAI CITY, YESTERDAY

19:54.600 --> 19:57.240
They survived an accident,
went into debt for treatment,

19:57.320 --> 19:58.960
and now someone hired a hit on them.

19:59.480 --> 20:01.600
The Xu's really have it rough.

20:01.680 --> 20:03.720
Let's just hope
nothing else happens to them.

20:06.520 --> 20:07.720
Hard to say.

20:07.800 --> 20:11.120
From the scene at their home,
they left in a hurry.

20:11.720 --> 20:14.360
But why would they go to Yuanlongli?

20:14.440 --> 20:16.720
And then disappear in the elevator?

20:17.680 --> 20:21.040
Something about this doesn't add up.

20:22.120 --> 20:23.360
Up till now,

20:23.440 --> 20:25.640
we still don't know how they disappeared.

20:27.040 --> 20:28.760
Let's hope nothing else happens to them.

20:28.840 --> 20:30.640
Otherwise, this case
could drag on forever.

20:36.040 --> 20:38.480
I'm heading to the video rental shop
Wolfie mentioned,

20:38.560 --> 20:39.400
see if I can dig up anything

20:39.480 --> 20:40.560
-about the person who hired the hit.
-Well.

20:40.640 --> 20:42.720
I think we should start
with the loan shark.

20:42.800 --> 20:44.880
Jin Manshan wasn't telling
the truth yesterday.

20:44.960 --> 20:46.480
He was definitely holding something back.

20:46.560 --> 20:48.440
We should press him
and get the truth out of him.

20:49.600 --> 20:51.400
Then you go find Jin Manshan.
I'll check out the video rental shop.

20:51.480 --> 20:54.440
That place is full of all kinds
of shady characters.

20:54.520 --> 20:56.600
Don't scare them off.

21:09.080 --> 21:10.080
Officer He.

21:11.040 --> 21:12.000
Hm?

21:13.640 --> 21:16.240
Actually, we can go together.

21:17.160 --> 21:18.880
Better to have each other's backs.

21:21.960 --> 21:23.320
That foot bath grossed you out that much?

21:24.720 --> 21:27.680
Sure. Call me "sir", and I'll go with you.

21:31.440 --> 21:33.240
He can't take a joke.

21:35.800 --> 21:38.000
WANXIANG VIDEO RENTAL SHOP

21:38.080 --> 21:40.840
CONTINUOUS SCREENINGS
NO ADDITIONAL TICKETS NEEDED

21:45.160 --> 21:46.320
RAN FANGXU POLICE ID

22:01.480 --> 22:03.920
Officers, this way, please.

22:04.000 --> 22:05.800
SCREENING ROOM

22:05.880 --> 22:08.560
TOP PICKS FROM HK
ACTION-PACKED WESTERNS

22:11.200 --> 22:12.440
The night before last,

22:12.520 --> 22:14.720
someone came in wearing a cap and a mask.

22:14.800 --> 22:15.680
Ring a bell?

22:17.120 --> 22:19.240
So many people come and go every day.

22:19.320 --> 22:20.800
How would I remember?

22:21.320 --> 22:23.720
Jin Manlang was here too.
You don't remember that either?

22:23.800 --> 22:25.200
I really don't know.

22:26.280 --> 22:28.400
We wouldn't dare mess
with those gangsters.

22:29.000 --> 22:29.840
You're lying.

22:29.920 --> 22:31.680
No way.

22:31.760 --> 22:34.160
How would I dare lie to you officers?

22:34.240 --> 22:35.880
-You!
-Hey.

22:35.960 --> 22:36.920
Ran.

22:37.000 --> 22:38.160
Come over.

22:48.240 --> 22:49.680
Nothing he says is true.

22:49.760 --> 22:51.720
He's just trying to get by.

22:51.800 --> 22:53.960
Pushing him won't help.
Everyone's got their struggles.

23:00.320 --> 23:01.440
This is a murder-for-hire case.

23:01.520 --> 23:02.800
Lives are on the line.

23:02.880 --> 23:05.720
If he won't cooperate,
I'll file for an investigation right now.

23:05.800 --> 23:07.280
Wait.

23:08.440 --> 23:09.400
Let me think.

23:11.040 --> 23:11.880
I'll think of a way.

23:29.760 --> 23:31.040
THE PLUM IN THE GOLDEN VASE

23:36.160 --> 23:37.120
This one looks interesting.

23:38.800 --> 23:40.200
I'll take it back
and watch it at the station.

23:41.160 --> 23:43.720
It talks about human desires.

23:43.800 --> 23:44.880
-Officer.
-What is it?

23:45.760 --> 23:48.160
Look at me. My head just cleared up.

23:48.240 --> 23:51.440
I do remember that guy wearing a mask.

23:52.040 --> 23:53.040
What did he look like?

23:53.120 --> 23:54.760
Black cap, white mask. Does that help?

23:56.160 --> 23:59.440
-How tall?
-I was sitting down. Couldn't tell.

23:59.520 --> 24:00.920
What was he watching?

24:01.000 --> 24:03.800
That's the strange part.
He didn't watch anything.

24:03.880 --> 24:04.920
He went straight to the back
after coming in.

24:05.000 --> 24:06.000
He said he was looking for the restroom.

24:06.080 --> 24:09.640
Then he talked to Wolf for a bit,
took a phone call, and left.

24:09.720 --> 24:11.520
How did he leave? Did he drive?

24:11.600 --> 24:13.200
I was sitting over there. I didn't see.

24:13.280 --> 24:14.280
You'd better be honest.

24:14.360 --> 24:16.120
I'm really good at faces.

24:17.920 --> 24:18.960
I really am.

24:22.640 --> 24:25.000
VIDEO RENTAL SHOP

24:35.880 --> 24:36.720
What's wrong?

24:37.760 --> 24:39.920
It won't help to worry.
Let's go find Jin Manshan.

24:40.960 --> 24:41.880
Get in.

25:21.920 --> 25:23.000
Mister.

25:24.480 --> 25:25.720
What is it?

25:31.120 --> 25:33.000
Please. What do you want?

25:33.080 --> 25:34.320
Relax.

25:35.680 --> 25:37.240
Just want to ask about someone.

25:37.320 --> 25:39.600
-Go on, please.
-Stay still.

25:51.480 --> 25:52.320
So many books.

25:53.560 --> 25:56.120
This is sold by weight.
We can get a good price for it.

26:10.840 --> 26:11.760
There's a ghost making noise.

26:17.360 --> 26:19.840
-Where?
-Over there.

26:53.320 --> 26:54.360
See it?

26:55.880 --> 26:58.400
You know, my memory's sharp.

26:59.240 --> 27:01.400
This is obviously
a drifters' resting spot.

27:01.920 --> 27:03.240
That doesn't prove anything.

27:04.040 --> 27:05.640
Why not?

27:05.720 --> 27:08.440
These two wooden stools
were on the 18th floor just now.

27:14.160 --> 27:16.680
Which means someone's been tailing us.

27:16.760 --> 27:17.720
Help!

27:18.360 --> 27:20.600
-Help!
-Help!

27:21.440 --> 27:23.120
-Help!
-Help!

27:23.200 --> 27:25.440
Don't come any closer!

27:26.080 --> 27:28.120
-Help…
-Help!

27:28.200 --> 27:30.200
Help…

27:30.800 --> 27:31.720
Stop!

27:34.440 --> 27:36.480
Sir! Sir!

27:48.640 --> 27:49.600
Ang!

27:50.600 --> 27:51.640
Ang!

27:52.680 --> 27:53.840
Ang!

27:54.360 --> 27:55.920
Is he okay?

27:56.440 --> 27:58.680
Ms. Wang, let's send
the boy to the hospital first.

27:58.760 --> 28:00.120
Quick. Get in.

28:00.200 --> 28:02.880
-What's going on with the victim?
-He's the suspect.

28:03.440 --> 28:04.560
These two are the victims.

28:04.640 --> 28:05.880
The kid attacked them with a knife.

28:05.960 --> 28:06.920
Good thing it was dull.

28:07.680 --> 28:08.760
Have you seen my dad?

28:10.440 --> 28:11.440
NEW YORK BLOCK

28:11.520 --> 28:14.320
-Dad, you're hurt too?
-Just a scratch. I'm fine.

28:15.360 --> 28:17.800
Where's Fangxu? He was just here.

28:24.720 --> 28:27.200
-Mr. He, are you alright?
-Just superficial.

28:27.280 --> 28:28.800
Xiaohe, take my car.

28:28.880 --> 28:30.040
Get your dad home to rest.

28:31.160 --> 28:32.560
I don't need you worrying about me.

28:33.360 --> 28:34.720
Who's worrying about you?

28:34.800 --> 28:36.280
Captain Zhao is taking us to the scene.

28:36.360 --> 28:37.480
Stop wandering around here.

28:38.080 --> 28:40.480
Jerk, I found the boy.

28:40.560 --> 28:42.000
What? Are you trying to take the credit?

28:42.080 --> 28:43.680
-Dad.
-No wonder you're bald.

28:45.120 --> 28:47.280
Living off other people's work.

28:49.920 --> 28:50.920
Ran!

28:52.640 --> 28:53.480
Ran!

28:54.520 --> 28:57.200
-Get in.
-Alright.

28:59.800 --> 29:00.640
Let's go.

29:32.880 --> 29:33.720
Why are we here?

29:34.800 --> 29:38.080
Isn't Jin Manshan's men
supposed to be at Jinsha Market?

29:39.440 --> 29:41.560
Being a beat officer takes skill.

29:41.640 --> 29:44.280
These 20 years weren't for nothing.

29:54.520 --> 29:57.000
LEIGONG STREET

30:03.240 --> 30:04.680
They've got a lookout.

30:09.360 --> 30:11.200
Play drunk. Can you do that?

30:19.200 --> 30:21.920
-I want more.
-Slow down.

30:22.000 --> 30:24.880
-Another carton.
-Watch the step. Slow down.

30:24.960 --> 30:26.920
I can drink another carton of beer.

30:27.640 --> 30:28.680
Wait.

30:28.760 --> 30:30.520
Why don't we just go in?

30:30.600 --> 30:31.440
Why make it so complicated?

30:32.040 --> 30:34.040
It's a small gambling den.

30:34.120 --> 30:36.160
I busted it before.

30:37.240 --> 30:39.320
This time, we'll just scare them a bit.

30:40.160 --> 30:42.440
-Slow down.
-I'm fine.

30:49.600 --> 30:51.200
His legs.

30:57.480 --> 30:58.920
Right here.

31:03.840 --> 31:05.920
Why is it you again, Officer He?

31:06.880 --> 31:07.840
Cut the crap.

31:07.920 --> 31:09.080
Is Jin Manshan inside?

31:10.400 --> 31:11.280
How many people?

31:12.200 --> 31:13.920
-Over 20.
-More than 20?

31:21.600 --> 31:22.440
Where are you going?

31:22.520 --> 31:23.560
Too many of them.

31:23.640 --> 31:25.400
We can't just rush in.
I need to check the layout first.

31:36.880 --> 31:38.600
Business looks pretty good lately.

31:39.120 --> 31:40.160
That's all the bosses.

31:40.240 --> 31:43.040
I just watch the door and keep lookout.

31:43.120 --> 31:46.240
Officer He,
please don't tell Mr. Jin it's me.

31:46.320 --> 31:49.360
You've got some nerve
to bargain with me, huh?

31:49.440 --> 31:50.800
If you have time, read a book.

31:50.880 --> 31:52.720
Or get a proper job in Guangzhou.

31:52.800 --> 31:54.720
Stop hanging around with these people.

31:54.800 --> 31:56.960
-Got it?
-Got it, Officer He.

32:04.640 --> 32:05.560
Listen up.

32:05.640 --> 32:08.160
When you go back in,
as soon as you hear a gunshot,

32:08.240 --> 32:10.080
shout "police are coming" four more times.

32:10.160 --> 32:11.960
Then hide. Stay out of sight
for a few days.

32:12.040 --> 32:13.440
When you come out,
just say you got detained.

32:13.520 --> 32:14.880
Understand?

32:14.960 --> 32:16.840
Officer He, you brought a gun?

32:16.920 --> 32:17.760
Mm.

32:17.840 --> 32:19.200
That's intense.

32:19.280 --> 32:21.200
Stop talking and move.

32:27.280 --> 32:29.400
There's a trash bin by the back door.

32:29.480 --> 32:32.560
I'll wait there
and catch anyone who slips out.

32:32.640 --> 32:35.280
You're taking the lead today.
Can you handle it?

32:35.360 --> 32:36.880
Don't just curry favor
with others all the time.

32:37.880 --> 32:40.440
If I hadn't carried his legs just now,
would you have handled it alone?

32:41.600 --> 32:43.200
Cut it out.

32:43.280 --> 32:45.160
Open fire when I'm in position.

32:47.120 --> 32:49.480
-What now?
-I've never seen Jin Manshan.

32:49.560 --> 32:50.920
What does he look like?

32:51.440 --> 32:54.480
Big gold chain around his neck.
Two gold teeth.

32:56.760 --> 32:58.440
Big gold chain. Gold teeth.

33:17.560 --> 33:18.960
Police are here!

33:20.240 --> 33:22.920
Police are here! Police!

33:23.000 --> 33:24.480
Police!

33:24.560 --> 33:26.520
Police are here!

33:43.400 --> 33:45.040
-Police are coming!
-Police are coming!

33:45.120 --> 33:47.760
-Run quickly. Police are coming!
-Police are here!

33:47.840 --> 33:50.160
-Run!
-Run quickly!

33:50.240 --> 33:51.560
Move it now!

33:52.600 --> 33:53.600
Big gold chain. Gold teeth.

34:13.679 --> 34:14.719
Jin Manshan!

34:15.360 --> 34:17.080
Not me. You got the wrong person.

34:28.280 --> 34:29.920
Police! Stay put!

34:32.920 --> 34:34.800
Stop running! Stand right there!

34:47.920 --> 34:50.040
Jin Manshan, stop!

34:50.120 --> 34:52.320
He Yuanhang! He Yuanhang!

34:53.840 --> 34:55.159
He Yuanhang!

35:00.480 --> 35:01.600
Stop running!

35:12.400 --> 35:14.800
Officer He, what is this?

35:14.880 --> 35:16.160
Why are you doing this?

35:16.240 --> 35:18.680
Also, what if the lamp post
leaks electricity?

35:18.760 --> 35:19.800
Cut the nonsense.

35:19.880 --> 35:21.800
Don't tell me you have no idea
why you're being cuffed.

35:21.880 --> 35:24.240
Yesterday afternoon,
when I asked about Xu Meng,

35:24.320 --> 35:25.440
why didn't you say anything?

35:25.520 --> 35:29.240
Officer He, I don't follow.

35:29.320 --> 35:30.680
Who is Xu Meng?

35:30.760 --> 35:32.520
She borrowed 8,000 from you.

35:32.600 --> 35:34.320
It has grown to 250,000 with interest.

35:34.400 --> 35:36.040
Does that jog your memory?

35:36.120 --> 35:37.520
I've got a lot of borrowers.

35:38.120 --> 35:40.720
I don't remember small fry like that.

35:40.800 --> 35:43.520
I only deal with big clients.

35:43.600 --> 35:45.040
Then why did you have
someone watching her house?

35:45.120 --> 35:48.000
Young man, you're really confusing me.

35:48.080 --> 35:50.320
I don't even know if Xu Meng
is a man or a woman.

35:50.400 --> 35:52.160
Why would I have someone watch her?

35:57.760 --> 36:00.120
Here. Take a look. Recognize this?

36:02.040 --> 36:04.120
I really have no idea.

36:04.200 --> 36:07.640
My guys handle small loans like 8,000.

36:08.440 --> 36:11.840
This wrench owes me money
and still runs off.

36:14.160 --> 36:15.760
Watch your mouth.

36:15.840 --> 36:17.440
She owes money and skips out.

36:17.520 --> 36:19.600
Why should I respect her?
Did she respect me?

36:19.680 --> 36:20.560
It's not even 10,000.

36:20.640 --> 36:23.240
She could've paid it back somehow.

36:23.320 --> 36:26.840
-Wrench. I'll catch her one day…
-Can't you talk without swearing?

36:26.920 --> 36:28.040
Huh?

36:29.160 --> 36:30.520
There you go again.

36:37.600 --> 36:38.600
You!

36:39.760 --> 36:42.600
Officer He, you're done asking.

36:42.680 --> 36:44.000
Let me ask you something.

36:46.120 --> 36:49.320
What did Jin Manlang do?

36:49.400 --> 36:51.120
Are you sure you don't know?

36:53.560 --> 36:56.680
Did that idiot run his mouth,
saying he killed someone?

36:57.400 --> 36:58.480
Don't believe him.

36:58.560 --> 37:00.440
He's been a coward since he was a kid.

37:00.520 --> 37:02.600
Too scared to kill a chicken,
and he talks about murder?

37:02.680 --> 37:04.280
He's just bluffing.

37:06.320 --> 37:08.000
You don't know your brother very well.

37:16.520 --> 37:17.640
Jin Manshan,

37:17.720 --> 37:19.520
you assaulted a police officer.

37:19.600 --> 37:21.240
I could detain you for that.

37:22.080 --> 37:23.160
But listen.

37:24.400 --> 37:27.280
If you can help me find out
what else the father and daughter

37:27.360 --> 37:29.680
were involved in,
besides borrowing from you,

37:29.760 --> 37:31.760
we'll count it as making up for it.

37:31.840 --> 37:33.200
Do you get what I mean?

37:33.880 --> 37:34.760
Yes.

37:41.600 --> 37:43.360
-Thank you.
-Hands.

37:44.680 --> 37:45.680
Don't forget that.

38:06.120 --> 38:07.280
Where are we going?

38:08.480 --> 38:09.760
I'll drop you back at the dorm.

38:11.400 --> 38:12.720
Let me off at a bus stop.

38:13.960 --> 38:16.200
It's late. There are no buses now.

38:22.240 --> 38:24.680
I've noticed you've been off today.

38:25.600 --> 38:27.520
I told you. Lack of sleep can mess you up.

38:27.600 --> 38:28.920
You never listen.

38:29.000 --> 38:31.640
Not enough sleep affects your judgment

38:31.720 --> 38:33.080
and makes you irritable.

38:34.000 --> 38:36.280
He was being disrespectful.
He had it coming.

38:49.560 --> 38:52.080
Pass me the stuff in the door handle.

39:00.440 --> 39:01.480
Stay-awake kit.

39:02.480 --> 39:04.000
My daughter got it for me.

39:09.200 --> 39:10.640
Your daughter sounds thoughtful.

39:11.680 --> 39:13.200
More than that.

39:13.720 --> 39:14.720
Want to try?

39:24.240 --> 39:26.120
Her teachers all say

39:26.640 --> 39:28.920
she takes after me.

39:29.680 --> 39:31.280
Quick-witted.

39:31.360 --> 39:33.600
The only problem is she's a bit stubborn.

39:34.280 --> 39:35.800
She's great at sports

39:35.880 --> 39:37.640
and loves figuring things out.

39:37.720 --> 39:38.880
Brains and brawn.

39:39.400 --> 39:40.480
Just like me.

39:41.360 --> 39:44.560
Do you think I should
let her join the police like me,

39:44.640 --> 39:47.040
or go into finance like her mom?

39:47.720 --> 39:49.240
Don't mind me talking so much.

39:49.320 --> 39:51.120
I'm driving at night.

39:51.200 --> 39:52.880
Talking keeps me awake.

39:54.200 --> 39:56.360
It's fine. Go on.

39:56.440 --> 39:59.280
Don't let me do the talking.
You say something too.

40:01.720 --> 40:03.120
Why did you come to Weiyang?

40:03.880 --> 40:05.440
My mom got married. I came with her.

40:07.160 --> 40:09.640
Right. You didn't finish
your story last time.

40:10.160 --> 40:12.320
What about you? What does your family do?

40:19.880 --> 40:21.480
Had a falling-out with them?

40:23.720 --> 40:27.080
You young people live so far from home.

40:27.840 --> 40:30.520
Your parents worry and nag a little.

40:30.600 --> 40:32.280
That's normal.

40:34.920 --> 40:36.240
They passed away.

41:23.880 --> 41:24.880
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

41:29.840 --> 41:31.000
Speak up.

41:31.080 --> 41:34.080
Mr. Jin, we were thinking
of staking out her place

41:34.160 --> 41:35.400
and handling it ourselves.

41:35.480 --> 41:36.520
Handling it yourselves?

41:37.480 --> 41:38.520
So, your solution

41:38.600 --> 41:41.840
is to let the police trace it back to me?

41:42.680 --> 41:43.720
-No. It's not like that.
-Mr. Jin.

41:43.800 --> 41:45.360
Mr. Jin. Mr. Jin.

41:46.720 --> 41:48.280
Mr. Jin, I brought him here.

41:48.360 --> 41:49.840
Morning, Mr. Jin.

41:50.840 --> 41:51.880
Get lost.

41:54.160 --> 41:55.200
Thank you.

41:55.280 --> 41:56.720
-Sit.
-Let's sit.

41:59.040 --> 42:01.680
What is the situation inside?
What did he say?

42:01.760 --> 42:03.920
Wolf is doing fine in there.
Food is decent.

42:04.000 --> 42:06.640
When he first got locked up,
he was bragging.

42:06.720 --> 42:07.600
He said he took out two people.

42:10.200 --> 42:12.720
How do you know he was bluffing?

42:12.800 --> 42:15.360
Mr. Jin, you know my nickname.

42:15.440 --> 42:16.480
Sharp Ears.

42:16.560 --> 42:19.480
When he first went in,
he clung to the bars and refused to move.

42:19.560 --> 42:21.240
He kept crying and told the warden

42:21.320 --> 42:22.880
that he didn't kill anyone.

42:22.960 --> 42:24.440
He only slaughtered a few chickens.

42:25.160 --> 42:26.000
Are you sure?

42:26.080 --> 42:28.440
Mr. Jin, I was locked up
for pickpocketing.

42:28.520 --> 42:30.600
If Wolf had killed someone,
he wouldn't be in the same place as me.

42:34.120 --> 42:36.360
You know the law pretty well.

42:37.240 --> 42:38.360
Thank you, Mr. Jin.

42:39.160 --> 42:40.080
By the way,

42:40.600 --> 42:42.520
the one who hired him,

42:44.240 --> 42:45.080
any news?

42:45.160 --> 42:47.240
Mr. Jin, I've sent people
to track him down.

42:49.680 --> 42:51.240
That dickhead.

42:53.240 --> 42:55.040
He set Manlang up.

42:55.720 --> 42:56.880
I'll make sure he pays for it.

42:56.960 --> 42:58.400
Yeah. Make him pay.

42:59.400 --> 43:00.240
Mr. Jin.

43:02.360 --> 43:03.400
What is it?

43:04.680 --> 43:06.560
The punk who set Wolf up

43:06.640 --> 43:07.680
has been found.

43:09.080 --> 43:10.040
Who is it?

43:10.120 --> 43:12.720
The video rental shop owner
didn't recognize him,

43:12.800 --> 43:13.840
but he remembers the car.

43:14.440 --> 43:16.880
A Mercedes. Plate ending in 688.

43:19.200 --> 43:20.760
688.

45:04.280 --> 45:07.960
PARKING GARAGE EXIT
